<br>
I challenge you to really look at this cause it's not the case at all.<br>
<br>
High level toons that are unguilded and with no reputation will almost never be invited to High End raids, especially High End Guild raids.<br>
<br>
Don't you have to EARN your way into a guild?<br>
<br>
And how do you do that?<br>
<br>
Don't you have to EARN officer's respect and then go on probationary types of periods even after you've established that respect?<br>
<br>
So this crazy notion that &quot;asshats&quot; are gonna change their name and then join High end raids only to do crazy shit is pretty ludicrous.<br>
<br>
High Level toons that are unguilded and also not known by the community will have to EARN their respect for that privelage.<br>
